title: Hidden In Plain Sight 6 - Why Three Dimensions (2016) Gooner
description:
Hidden In Plain Sight 6 - Why Three Dimensions (2016) (Epub) Gooner

Publisher: CreateSpace Independent Publishing Platform (12 July 2016)
Language: English
ISBN-10: 1534711910
ISBN-13: 978-1534711914

Why are there three dimensions of space? It is surprising that science does not know the answer, though there have been some inventive and controversial ideas. This book considers many of those ideas and presents a new solution why three is the magic number
